Industry News


                Banking & Financial Services            


Exclusive: 'Shark Tank'-backed startup confirms change at the top (Video)




Oct 29, 2015, 1:54pm EDT



Updated Oct 29, 2015, 3:54pm EDT






Industries & Tags


                    Banking & Financial Services,                 


            Private equity             














Patty Tascarella


Senior Reporter
Pittsburgh Business Times













                    Share
                


























 Order Reprints


 Save Article




 Print
















 



 Email




 Facebook




 LinkedIn




 Twitter




 Save Article





More 






 Email




 Facebook




 LinkedIn




 Order Reprints




