Industry News


                Manufacturing            


PittMoss growing production — and hiring — with capital raise (Video)




Feb 9, 2015, 2:39pm EST



Updated Feb 9, 2015, 5:40pm EST






Industries & Tags


                    Manufacturing,                 



                    Banking & Financial Services,                 



                    Career & Workplace,                 


            Startups             














Patty Tascarella


Senior Reporter
Pittsburgh Business Times













